episodes.title: Former MAGA Member Exposes Trump Cult Psychology | Breaking Free from Christian Nationalism
episodes.description:
In this powerful exposé, Jenny Gage reveals how she escaped the grips of Christian nationalism and Trump's MAGA movement. Through therapy and critical thinking, she uncovered the cult-like psychology behind these ideologies. Learn how religious trauma and political radicalization intersect to create dangerous belief systems. Support our channel for more evidence-based analysis of extremist movements.
